{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/about/layout,_N_T_/about/page,_N_T_/about"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><!--cCj4UeKrK1USe3QA_mCxC--><html lang=\"en\" class=\"__variable_188b3f __variable_8b3a0b __variable_6d24ac\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/a4546f67ddbda619.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-05173f67f96f24be.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-c023c6e3521b1417.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/255-3981a3d1f3561bd8.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-3d02345fdecf95ee.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/297-acf454feea2a9bd2.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/991-2cd1508f99913a78.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/layout-50582bb78ce4b3e8.js\" async=\"\"></script><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://upload-widget.cloudinary.com/global/all.js\" as=\"script\"/><title>About — OPINIONPLUS</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"A platform to tell your story, with your name and logo at the top, and the tools to build an audience around your truth.\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"font-body bg-paper text-ink min-h-screen flex flex-col antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><header class=\"border-b border-wire bg-paper/95 backdrop-blur sticky top-0 z-40\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between h-16\"><a class=\"flex items-baseline gap-2 group\" href=\"/\"><span class=\"editorial-h text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight\">OPINION<span class=\"text-signal\">PLUS</span></span><span class=\"hidden sm:inline wire-tag\">every voice, a masthead</span></a><nav class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-6 text-sm font-medium\"><a class=\"hover:text-signal transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Feed</a><a class=\"btn-primary px-4 py-2 text-sm rounded-sm\" href=\"/login\">Sign in</a></nav><button class=\"md:hidden\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\"><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"12\" y2=\"12\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"6\" y2=\"6\"></line><line x1=\"4\" x2=\"20\" y1=\"18\" y2=\"18\"></line></svg></button></div></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"max-w-2xl mx-auto px-5 py-16\"><p class=\"wire-tag mb-3\">About</p><h1 class=\"editorial-h text-4xl font-bold mb-8\">Every voice deserves a masthead.</h1><div class=\"prose-story text-ink-700 text-[1.05rem]\"><p>Most platforms ask you to shrink your story to fit a feed. OpinionPlus starts from the opposite instinct: your name goes at the top, your logo sits beside it, and the page belongs to you before it belongs to an algorithm.</p><p>We built OpinionPlus for the journalist without a masthead, the filmmaker without a distributor, and the person who simply has something true to say and nowhere that feels like theirs to say it. A story here isn&#x27;t a post lost in a scroll — it&#x27;s a publication with your byline, your archive, and readers who chose to follow you specifically.</p><p>That&#x27;s the whole idea, really. Give people the tools a real publisher would have — logo, profile, engagement, an audience — and get out of the way. The stories are yours. We just built the newsroom.</p><p>OpinionPlus is moderated, not policed. Admins exist to handle abuse and false reports, not to referee opinions. If your story is true and it&#x27;s yours, it belongs here.</p></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"border-t border-wire mt-24\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 py-12 grid gap-10 sm:grid-cols-3\"><div><p class=\"editorial-h text-xl font-extrabold\">OPINION<span class=\"text-signal\">PLUS</span></p><p class=\"text-sm text-ink-400 mt-2 max-w-xs\">A platform where every person gets a masthead — their name, their logo, their truth, at the top of the page.</p></div><div><p class=\"wire-tag mb-3\">Read</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-signal\" href=\"/\">Feed</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-signal\" href=\"/about\">About OpinionPlus</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"wire-tag mb-3\">Legal &amp; support</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-signal\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy policy</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-signal\" href=\"/contact\">Contact us</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"rule\"><p class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-5 py-5 text-xs text-ink-400\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> OpinionPlus. Every byline belongs to the person who wrote it.</p></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-05173f67f96f24be.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[7768,[\\\"297\\\",\\\"static/chunks/297-acf454feea2a9bd2.js\\\",\\\"991\\\",\\\"static/chunks/991-2cd1508f99913a78.js\\\",\\\"177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-50582bb78ce4b3e8.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n3:I[6128,[\\\"297\\\",\\\"static/chunks/297-acf454feea2a9bd2.js\\\",\\\"991\\\",\\\"static/chunks/991-2cd1508f99913a78.js\\\",\\\"177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-50582bb78ce4b3e8.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[9766,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n5:I[8924,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n6:I[2619,[\\\"297\\\",\\\"static/chunks/297-acf454feea2a9bd2.js\\\",\\\"991\\\",\\\"static/chunks/991-2cd1508f99913a78.js\\\",\\\"177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-50582bb78ce4b3e8.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\nb:I[7150,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/css/a