agement, an audience — and get out of the way. The stories are yours. We just built the newsroom.\"}]\n8:[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"OpinionPlus is moderated, not policed. Admins exist to handle abuse and false reports, not to referee opinions. If your story is true and it's yours, it belongs here.\"}]\n9:[\"$\",\"$Lc\",null,{\"children\":[\"$Ld\",[\"$\",\"$Le\",null,{\"promise\":\"$@f\"}]]}]\na:[\"$\",\"$1\",\"h\",{\"children\":[null,[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"children\":\"$L11\"}],null],[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"hidden\":true,\"children\":[\"$\",\"$13\",null,{\"fallback\":null,\"children\":\"$L14\"}]}]}]]}]\n11:[[\"$\",\"meta\",\"0\",{\"charSet\":\"utf-8\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"viewport\",\"content\":\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"}]]\nd:null\nf:{\"metadata\":[[\"$\",\"title\",\"0\",{\"children\":\"About — OPINIONPLUS\"}],[\"$\",\"meta\",\"1\",{\"name\":\"description\",\"content\":\"A platform to tell your story, with your name and logo at the top, and the tools to build an audience around your truth.\"}]],\"error\":null,\"digest\":\"$undefined\"}\n14:\"$f:metadata\"\n"}